OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSteve Wright hosts final   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRadio 2 afternoon show     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Steve Wright told listeners to his     
OL,6, final daily BBC Radio 2 programme that 
OL,7, he wants to "celebrate the show's      
OL,8, success and long run" after 23 years.  
OL,10,FThe DJ delivered a heartfelt speech    
OL,11,Fduring the final edition of Steve      
OL,12,FWright in the Afternoon on Friday.     
OL,14,FHe said: "I want to say thank you to   
OL,15,Fyou for your appreciation, our dearest 
OL,16,Flistener smashing and loyal, for all   
OL,17,Fthe reaction and all the nice words."  
OL,19,FHe stressed that he was not retiring,  
OL,20,Fand will keep his Sunday morning show. 
